by NM Bryan Tillis, author of our Chessable opening course Master the French.} *

[Event "Short & Sweet: The French Defense"]
[Site "Main Level"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
[Round "?"]
[White "French Introduction"]
[Black "?"]
[Result "*"]
[SourceTitle "Main Level"]
